        • gField

          GField gField
          Composite gravitational field, which groups all gravitional field generating objects within a wrapper class that simplifies field querying. Queries are either total, or exclude a single object, which is useful when computing the value of the field experienced by that object, due to all others.
          See Also:
          GField

        • bField

          BField bField
          Composite magnetic field, which groups all magnetic field generating objects within a wrapper class that simplifies field querying. Queries are either total, or exclude a single object, which is useful when computing the value of the field experienced by that object, due to all others.
          See Also:
          BField

        • eField

          EField eField
          Composite electric field, which groups all electric field generating objects within a wrapper class that simplifies field querying. Queries are either total, or exclude a single object, which is useful when computing the value of the field experienced by that object, due to all others.
          See Also:
          EField

        • pField

          PField pField
          Composite Pauli field, which groups all Pauli field generating objects within a wrapper class that simplifies field querying. Queries are either total, or exclude a single object, which is useful when computing the value of the field experienced by that object, due to all others.
          See Also:
          PField
